Thanks!

Keep Up The Good Work!
Congrats on 400, I have no idea how you find them all but keep up the good work.  So many new and interesting groups I would never have heard had it not been for your packs.  :)

Another century!
Many thanks for this fantastic piece of work and for the many hours of enjoyment and my enlightment to many new and unheard of bands.
Cheers
